          PsiPodVerbatimParagraphImpl(Perl5 POD: POD_VERBATIM_PARAGRAPH)
            PsiElement(Perl5 POD: code)('    U8 *utf;     /* Initialize this to point to the beginning of the\n                    sequence to convert */\n    U8 *utf_end; /* Initialize this to 1 beyond the end of the sequence\n                    pointed to by 'utf' */\n    UV uv;\t /* Returned code point; note: a UV, not a U8, not a\n                    char */\n    STRLEN len; /* Returned length of character in bytes */\n\n    if (!UTF8_IS_INVARIANT(*utf))\n        /* Must treat this as UTF-8 */\n        uv = utf8_to_uvchr_buf(utf, utf_end, &len);\n    else\n        /* OK to treat this character as a byte */\n        uv = *utf;\n')
